. Red marks pointing to transverse ridge in 
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="141">A-D</emphasis>
blue marks pointing to second transverse ridge in 
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="141">C, D</emphasis>
